name: FUEL
description: iRocket is a play and earn GameFi project that brings web3 entertainment to the masses with physical and virtual prizes. Play and accumulate reward points to unlock exciting prizes, exclusive yield bonuses. Redeem your points for virtual and physical rewards, such as in-game items, merchandise, gift cards, and more. Players can earn more from the game by staking their $FUEL tokens (Fuel Deposits) to boost rewards.
